// Replay reject pin: a sorry-containing discharge must never be
// admitted. The factored checker names the check
// (CHECK-FAIL: sorry-in-user-file); the axiom audit would catch the
// resulting sorryAx even if the text scan were bypassed.
enable_experimental;
fails (prove_print (offline_lean_replay "rejected_proof")
  {{ \(x : [8]) (y : [8]) -> x + y == y + x }});
